    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Bash your<strong> lemongrass</strong> with a<strong> rolling pin</strong>, then remove the <strong>tough outer layer[s]</strong> and set aside for later</p><p>Chop the <strong>softer inner core[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
