    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Return the<strong> pulled chicken</strong> to the pan with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good stir – this is your <strong>free range chicken tom kha soup</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
